


steps:


** Paste your schema.prisma file under prisma/ folder


** paste this code in the header of file :
generator dbml {
  provider = "prisma-dbml-generator"
}

** remove db_url from source db { ... }



** Run the command below to generate the DBML file
```bash
npx prisma generate
```
** The generated DBML file will be located at prisma/dbml/schema.dbml